									<children>
										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="AnimationTags" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="[ChristianD] as Player struggling to regain control of their body, they rigidly raise their hand and lift up the corpse., , [ShiPei] The player from the mindmeld postion sudddely feels a jolt in their body. They suddenly feel they have no control in their body and thus their body action &amp; movement becomes rigid. Someone is controlling their body. They then raise their hand and the corpse lift up in to mid air. The force action is similar to the action of SN: CINE_SpeakWithDead_Speaker_02_Start &amp; SN: CINE_SpeakWithDead_Speaker_02_Loop except is more rigid as their action is not of their own" />
										</node>
										<node id="data">
