											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="AnimationTags" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="[ChristianD] As the compulsion takes over, the Player clenches their hand into a fist and twists the corpse's neck. Player shocked and reacted horribly. A tadpole then burst out from one of the corpse's eye and floats to player's hand. As soon as the tadpole reaches the player hands, the spells breaks and the corpse drops down to the ground. Out of exhaustion, player drops down on both knees and gets up on both feet., , , The player feels a jerk and then clench their hand in to a fist. The corpse in mid-air starts to jerk and twist. The player is shock and horrified to see this. Then a tadpole bursts out of the corpse eye and floats to the player's hand. As soon as the tadpole reach the player hands, the spells break and the corpse drops down to the floor" />
										</node>
